title: MFSL UDCD SPECIAL 24KT GOLD PACK #10 ALAC
description: Here are the sound check and proper JS-1 JS-1A and 501. I made a mistake with the previous 501. It is actually JS-1. I have included an image of the sound check which is CDDA as well. The MFCD collection will not be complete but will be about 70% I think. A very obscure collection.
